HEADWORD: Metallurgy
<hw>Met"al*lur`gy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>m⟦eacute⟧tallurgie</ets>, fr. L. <ets>metallum</ets> metal, Gr. <?/
a mine + the root of <?/ work. See <er>Metal</er>, and
<er>Work</er>.]</ety> <def>The art of working metals, comprehending the
